{
  "chapter": 45,
  "chapter_summary": "第45章《一剑仇》讲述了芮玮与老农的对话。老农向芮玮解释了叶士谋送来服侍他的农夫的情况，以及他们学会生吃毒蛇的行为。芮玮询问这些农夫是否也被施过术，老农予以否认。章节中出现了芮玮、老农、叶士谋、道士归真等人物，涉及竹剑、剑招等武功技巧。老农展示了独特的剑法，能用竹剑击败持利剑的道士。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁是你的小兄弟！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错呀！否则他们怎肯安心住在谷中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，你心肠不错，我还真不愿与你比剑呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮豪然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们以死相拼，用不着相让。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农一声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "归真，看剑！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "道士不像先前茫然无动于衷，惊举起剑来，一剑挡去，两剑相交，\"当\"的一声，老农虽是竹剑，却无丝毫损伤，反见",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农手腕微微一旋，",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农并不阻止，让他拾剑，一等拾起",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁树开花",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁树开花",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "归真失血太多，手臂一软，宝剑\"咣当\"落地，老农杀得兴起，已失名家剑手风范，飒飒剑光不止，顷刻就在归真身上添了十余",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咣当",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮持剑举",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要歇歇，还是现在就比。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然现在就比。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮见他脸色仍未恢复过来，摇头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不成，等下再比。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小子，你瞧不起老夫吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮平静",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是，咱们要战得公平。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮走到归真身前，扶起他来，只见归真的伤势无可挽救，他睁开血肉模糊的眼皮，忽然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "邪剑……邪剑……好厉害的邪剑……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈，你的伤势甚重，好好养息不要说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "归真微弱地摆头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要死了，邪……邪剑……未死，烦你……转告江湖……要他们注意……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮轻轻放下归真，心中回旋那句\"邪剑未死\"的话，这句话与法海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "邪剑未死",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农铁青着脸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是又怎样！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你在跟谁说话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是在教训老夫吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是敢，也只能最后说这些话了。看剑！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农一语不发，忽地",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你每天都要吃吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农点头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一天不吃都不行，今天只因多用了点真力，才吃一条赤尾蛇，毒又发作出来，还好箩中还剩一条雨伞节，不然……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农仰望苍天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是天下第一毒，金菊花！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮惊呼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金菊花！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道金菊花吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "不由大声",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁下的毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "老农悲愤地",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张玉珍！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是她！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么？你认识她？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "认识，我听说她曾用金菊花害死天下第一高手胡一刀……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_nong",
      "speaker_name": "老农",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，想不到你年纪虽轻也知道了这件武林轶事，张玉珍害死胡一刀，没几年找上了我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是看上你那套邪剑啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮惊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这下糟了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么糟了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮愤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她这种人淫毒无比，心比蛇蝎还毒！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮大声吼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仇比天高，倾四海水洗之不净！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道不报此仇？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你那更强的仇敌是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰咬牙切齿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是我那更强的仇敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是大师伯救了贼尼一命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叶士谋在利用你呀！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮摇头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就不能不杀吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰正色",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只知你姓芮，不知你叫什么，能见告吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下单名玮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我能叫你小兄弟吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我哪里有对你好！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "郭少峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个么嘛，我也说不上来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我劝你能不能不要再杀人报仇？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "芮玮一怔，忽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的毒伤，我能帮你解去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    }
  ],
